This is a bot for the Direct Connect(DC++) protocol written in ruby.
rDCbot was tested for ruby 1.8.7

Usage:

require 'lib/rdcbot'

hub_address = '10.8.13.88'
hub_port    = 8888

bot = RDCbot.new
bot.nickname = 'rdcBot'
bot.description = 'http://github.com'
bot.host = hub_address
bot.port = hub_port
bot.email = 'github@gmail.com'

bot.start

sleep(1)
bot.say "test"
while bot.alive?
  sleep(3)
end
